content.rendered:
Directed by Vishwas Paandya

Written by Vishwas Paandya

Cast Anupam Kher (Charudutt Sharma / Charlie). Annu Kapoor (Brian Morris / Santa Claus). Manish Paul (Baba). Kay Kay Menon (ACP Shivraj Naik). Manjari Fadnnis (Angelina Morris (as Manjari Phadnis)). Manish Wadhwa (Utpal Shivalkar). Natasha Suri (Kamya). Sahil Vaid (Ashish Shivalkar). Aakash Dabhade (Fixer). Vineet Sharma (Daniel) . B Shantanu (Main Villain)

Languages Hindi

Producers Anand Swarup Agarwal. Krishna Datla. Debendra Jagadala
